      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How Amazon Macie Works\n\n1️⃣ Macie scans S3 buckets\n2️⃣ It analyzes the data using machine learning\n3️⃣ Detects sensitive information\n4️⃣ Generates security findings\n5️⃣ Alerts administrators",
